Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:12.38,中,NTP,0,0,0,,按照預知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.54,中,NTP,0,0,0,,把車胎打爆讓他停車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:18.43,中,NTP,0,0,0,,躲開了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:21.35,中,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是11th的日記預知到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:22.81,中,NTP,0,0,0,,可能和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:25.14,中,NTP,0,0,0,,是能預知周圍情況的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:26.31,中,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:29.12,中,NTP,0,0,0,,不能預知自己事情的可能性很高
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:31.62,中,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 直接攻擊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:34.23,中,NTP,0,0,0,,好險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:37.85,中,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的狀況也能預知嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:38.89,中,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:47.66,中,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊 這傢伙的日記
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:50.29,中,NTP,0,0,0,,想這樣讓我停車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:53.35,中,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣蠻幹可不像你啊 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:11.17,中,NTP,0,0,0,,起來 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:13.53,中,NTP,0,0,0,,雪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:16.07,中,NTP,0,0,0,,快點 這是機會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:25.55,中,NTP,0,0,0,,我們贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:28.58,中,NTP,0,0,0,, 那可不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:33.40,中,NTP,0,0,0,,按照預知 同伴現在正趕過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:35.20,中,NTP,0,0,0,,你的同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:38.74,中,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是你們的同伴 2nd
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:39.97,中,NTP,0,0,0,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.57,中,NTP,0,0,0,,秋瀨或
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:02.73,中,NTP,0,0,0,,哎喲 所有人在那裡不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:05.84,中,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:08.70,中,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡有股有趣的氣息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:11.51,中,NTP,0,0,0,,我在半路載上這傢伙之後 去了趟鑑定科
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:14.73,中,NTP,0,0,0,,再根據警察的無線聯絡把他送到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:16.47,中,NTP,0,0,0,,鑑定科？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:17.84,中,NTP,0,0,0,,我妻同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.99,0:20:21.83,中,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到和第三具屍體的DNA一致的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.96,中,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:29.11,中,NTP,0,0,0,,雪輝君 打開看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:37.45,中,NTP,0,0,0,, 這種東西都…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:39.46,中,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:44.19,中,NTP,0,0,0,,是放在我妻同學長大的那家養護設施裡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:46.29,中,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 你的意思是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:50.89,中,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊 是我妻同學的臍帶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.99,中,NTP,0,0,0,,這種東西都…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:55.07,中,NTP,0,0,0,,在鑑定科
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:21:00.33,中,NTP,0,0,0,,請他們將臍帶的DNA和第三具屍體比較了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:04.83,中,NTP,0,0,0,,其結果 二者的DNA完全一致
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:07.89,中,NTP,0,0,0,,你說謊 不要聽他的 雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:11.46,中,NTP,0,0,0,,DNA是…一致的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:17.41,中,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 即二者基因相同 是同一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:19.05,中,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:21.83,中,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 不是的 不是的 雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:25.87,中,NTP,0,0,0,,第三具屍體的真面目是我妻由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:29.00,中,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的她已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:33.19,中,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 但是 由乃她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:35.23,中,NTP,0,0,0,,我來說結論吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:38.70,中,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的那個她是假的我妻由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:42.36,中,NTP,0,0,0,,雪輝君 快離開她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:45.32,中,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 不是的 雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.48,0:21:47.90,中,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:51.62,中,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我 雪 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:58.22,中,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 不要 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.78,0:22:03.04,中,NTP,0,0,0,,雪…雪——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:49.96,中,NTP,0,0,0,,[數據傳送]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,中,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:03.93,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,The girl with the sharp thorn in her flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:06.28,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,I meet you at your story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:11.29,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Behind the hatred there lies a murderous love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.43,0:02:16.80,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you kill your friends, if you can fulfill your wish
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:19.29,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Can you die for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:22.43,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,They are synonymous words
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:27.69,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Life is a game It's a survival That's right! How do you start
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:33.19,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Time and Space It's a crossroad through a gate! Where do you go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:35.72,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,You seek eternal breath
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:37.88,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Why do you need to live
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:42.85,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,We don't know when this world came into being
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:45.13,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,We are the timeleaper
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:48.03,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Nothing's gonna change with you in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:51.04,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Everything will be decided by the rules
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:55.91,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, We are traveling the past and the future through love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:56.42,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Break out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:01.07,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's dial back all the pains and we will be born again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:04.12,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,I wanna see the stars with you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:07.27,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,Over the miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:13.87,op2en,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not a Dead END
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,日_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:03.93,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,帶刺的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:06.28,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我在你的故事裡認識你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:11.29,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,恨之深皆因愛之切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.43,0:02:16.80,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你會為一己之利置朋友於死地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:19.29,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,你會為了他人而犧牲自我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:22.43,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,它們又有何區別
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:27.69,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯！人生就是生存遊戲　你要如何開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:33.19,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,時間和空間是分岔路口　你要往哪走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:35.72,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,尋求永生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:37.88,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但生存的意義又是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:42.85,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我們並不知道世界的起點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:45.13,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只是時空的亂入者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:48.03,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,世界不會因你而改變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:51.04,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,規則才決定著一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:55.91,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，我們憑著愛穿越古今
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:56.42,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,爆發吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:03:01.07,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們浴火重生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:04.12,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和你一起看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:07.27,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,在奇蹟之後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:13.87,op2cn,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是終結
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.43,0:22:43.18,日_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,あとどれくらい失えば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.37,0:22:48.22,日_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,高鳴る鼓動許される?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:59.52,日_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,会いたくて涙 溢れるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:05.12,日_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,全ては未来を繋ぐ鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.26,0:23:12.74,日_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,崩れる身体に絆感じて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:25.15,日_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,もう一度君を守ると誓う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.43,0:22:43.18,中_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟還要失去多少
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.37,0:22:48.22,中_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,這劇烈的心悸方能被寬恕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:59.52,中_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,想要見到你 想到熱淚盈眶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:05.12,中_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是連接著未來的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.26,0:23:12.74,中_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,感到崩壞身體的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:25.15,中_ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我願意 再一次守護你 許下誓言
